pact on the gravity-only run and we\nhighlight the importance of better understanding this issue in hydrodynamic\napplications. This is the first in a simulation campaign using CRK-SPH with\nfuture work including subresolution gas treatments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Nov 2018 18:26:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Jun 2019 19:16:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-05"}
